msgid ""
"If you are outside the US, we recommend NOWPayments (lowest fees, direct to "
"your wallet). If you are in the US, Stripe Crypto is also an option. You can"
" enable multiple services and let your visitors choose!"
msgstr ""
"Als ge buiten de US zijt, raden wi NOWPayments aan (laagste fees, direkt na "
"uw wallet). Als ge in de US zijt, is Stripe Crypto oké 'n optie. Ge kan "
"meerdere dienste inschakelen en laat uw bezoekers kiezen!"

