msgid ""
"A powerful, free donation and payment widget that allows your visitors to "
"support you via credit card or cryptocurrency (Quai). No monthly fees, no "
"third-party subscriptions – just your wallet and free services."
msgstr ""
"Een sterk, gratis donatie- en betaal-widget die jo's bezoekers to laat "
"stuttjoar deur kredietkaart of cryptocurrency (Quai). Geen maandelike "
"heffingen, geen derde-partij abonnements – enkel jo wallet en gratis "
"dienste."

msgid ""
"Some browsers block third-party scripts for privacy. This proxy loads "
"scripts through your own server to bypass these blocks."
msgstr ""
"Sommige browsers blokkeert derde-partij scripts veur privacy. Deze proxy "
"laadt scripts deur jo eigen server om disse blokkades te omzeilen."

